title: Geoff Tate
itunes:title: Geoff Tate
description:
My HoneyDew this week is Geoff Tate! Geoff’s dad died last year. They had a complicated relationship and now Geoff doesn’t know why he does stand up. We also talk about Geoff’s divorce and how he quit drinking and went to therapy at the same time after his last big break up. Geoff goes deep! Subscribe, download & review!
